It is good to work with DBMS in our PHP site and it will help you to store your data correctly and well organized manner. 
Here I recommend "MySql" for the task. As MySql also open source it is very helpfull for the operations
Some of the benifits of having MySql.
  1. MySQL is the world's most popular open source database. 
  2. With its proven performance, reliability and ease-of-use, MySQL has become the leading database choice for web-based applications, used by high profile web properties including Facebook, Twitter, YouTube, Yahoo! and many more.
  3. Oracle drives MySQL innovation, delivering new capabilities to power next generation web and cloud.
  4. Also Support to Mobile and embedded applications.
  
